# This file keeps the icons/ folder in Git
# 
# Git does not track empty folders. This file ensures
# the icons folder exists in the repository so you can
# add your PWA icons later.
# 
# To replace this file with actual icons:
# 1. Generate icons using PWA Icon Generator
# 2. Upload them to this folder
# 3. Remove this .gitkeep file when icons are added
# 
# Required icons for PWA:
# - icon-72x72.png
# - icon-96x96.png
# - icon-128x128.png
# - icon-144x144.png
# - icon-152x152.png
# - icon-192x192.png
# - icon-384x384.png
# - icon-512x512.png
# 
# You can generate all sizes at:
# https://www.pwabuilder.com/imageGenerator
